Comment: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,########Screen_text########
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是布耶尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.61,0:00:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么玩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.83,0:02:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买下...和平？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.20,0:02:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 要不要试试用你的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买下这座岛的小小和平呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:18.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪某些笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:23.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们公司的机器人失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.30,0:02:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就因为这样 现在城市面临崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.31,0:02:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为「布耶尔」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.14,0:02:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们公司的巨大地质调查机器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.56,0:02:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保龄球机器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被她骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可远不止是台地质调查机器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要让它停下来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:49.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能平息这场骚动了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 现在只有你能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭我这样做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 你也需要克拉里昂的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:02:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:03.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你们二人齐心合力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.21,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能阻止布耶尔的失控
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.59,0:03:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 克拉玲的手臂还没...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.01,0:03:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.02,0:03:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.94,0:03:20.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.69,0:03:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和克拉里昂一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮帮...帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和克拉玲一起起起起...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只有我能做到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈判成立
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 来说一下作战计划吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潘多拉装置的使用时间限制让人担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.34,0:03:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 关于我具体想让你做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂 报告布耶尔的周边情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布耶尔的位置已确定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.56,0:04:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在瓦尔甘市边缘区的G11号地下矿洞中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:08.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处于地下约350米处的基层区
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.94,0:04:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那么深的地下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是布耶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼珠？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然眼珠才是浪漫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 消停了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变回原样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂 整理攻略布耶尔的作战方式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.93,0:04:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布耶尔的荷电粒子炮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发射后的冷却时间为180余秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为过热 冷却效率有所降低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以会逐渐延长几秒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太生硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再柔和些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.57,0:04:51.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.74,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 使用武力向布耶尔进行挑衅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱导其发射主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.37,0:05:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁其冷却时接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.00,0:05:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它停止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臣妾做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.88,0:05:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要回家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.96,0:05:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它停下 需要呼出它的中央控制台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用认证秘钥即可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.59,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘钥就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然是那个！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.06,0:05:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个就由我来做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那是克拉里昂的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音负责掩护克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音就用这个来掩护克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:35.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:38.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是我们挖到保管库的最快速度了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.58,0:05:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然还是试作品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.70,0:05:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但非常适合掩护克拉里昂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.58,0:05:46.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威力很强吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:48.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在定睛的瞬间击中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:55.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音 希望你别对这种说法感到不适
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.30,0:05:58.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这装备并不是血肉之躯能够驾驭的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有1分钟就要开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在紧张 必须冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.21,0:06:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 你不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.92,0:06:22.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「恐惧」的话 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.55,0:06:26.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不试试用勇气买下和平吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞 只要和克拉玲在一起 我就不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吵　　
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大厦崩塌 街道上伤佛混乱的大熔炉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,焦烟呛人的大危机
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞南库尔岛上究竟发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼见的不一定是真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.32,0:06:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相不一定如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为非常悲伤 所以说了两遍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑暗深处究竟潜伏着何种阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.66,0:06:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为您带来报道的正是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「最强最大！泰坦TV」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.66,0:07:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得骄傲的超大型偶像系究极媒体创作者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:05.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布一一玲一一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.09,0:07:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上还不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.22,0:07:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,壮士一去不复还
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用重武器施加压力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诱发主炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:38.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它怒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.33,0:07:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做诱饵很危险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.62,0:07:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 福音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要快速避开就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就行了...行了...了...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布耶尔进入了非常冷却模式
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好戏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.52,0:08:05.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是咒语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.37,0:08:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何人接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它都会进行无差别防御
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音的任务是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.41,0:09:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,@# ￥%...&*
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚上阵就这么能打
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.26,0:09:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人外有人 天外有天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实验室还没挖到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.89,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚挖通了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.20,0:09:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂 就在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 福音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:09:58.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天花板附近有紧急端口
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能启动那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:06.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就有可能接通外部了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:14.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央控制台...吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什...么...鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说真没礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间了就别在意细节了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.78,0:10:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂 快使用秘钥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.54,0:10:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:38.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个戴上去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.89,0:10:54.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:21.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.03,0:11:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平安的咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 克拉玲也一定...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接命中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南无...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 好像赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我努力挖出来的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 鸡蛋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙叫盖尔切克马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像克拉里昂的宠物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌泽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克...克拉玲她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂的话没事的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.06,0:12:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为操纵它们的就是克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那克拉玲在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.99,0:12:58.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这状态下 亏她还能分出战力给福音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 她还保持着优先保护福音的设定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.42,0:13:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她进入了布耶尔的防御圈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.97,0:13:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔切克马们 掩护她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音竟然有那么强的机动性
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 她并不是在躲避
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是通过逆用技能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预测到了布耶尔的射击界限
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.86,0:13:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来福音的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并不只是全身义体适合者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更有可能是别的「什么」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.24,0:13:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没法再靠近了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.21,0:13:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.13,0:13:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须快点到克拉里昂身边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我过去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掩护她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.99,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.33,0:14:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 再等一下 我马上救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂好像动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.13,0:14:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音去把布耶尔停下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.84,0:14:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点　　
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音是克拉里昂的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去吧 为了世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.81,0:14:51.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明白福音的正确使用方法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那个自尊心奇高的克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然会指望别人的援助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.91,0:15:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了克拉玲和世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让布耶尔停下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.96,0:15:17.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把眼镜给石像戴上就行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石像...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.30,0:15:25.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 因为我很能干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:28.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以预料到了这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:31.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑个喜欢的戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.69,0:15:35.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就设置成可外部操作的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.52,0:15:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.74,0:15:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该乖乖停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.76,0:16:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停下了...吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子真能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.59,0:16:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 看到了有趣的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说还想继续欣赏下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是说这话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.69,0:16:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心闹大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紧急撤退程序启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.57,0:16:25.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.16,0:16:30.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音 帮我回收认证秘钥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要断开「中央神经组件」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:39.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我小心回收它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.13,0:16:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中央...神经？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.96,0:16:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回收完毕后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻回收克拉里昂并撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.15,0:16:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾乃布耶尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是汝将吾从漫长恶梦中救出的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.03,0:17:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.44,0:17:06.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 大概
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫福音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.45,0:17:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音 吾赐汝以褒奖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「中央神经组件」是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是吾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.50,0:17:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明让你别动了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.50,0:17:25.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回复正常模式而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不准动 克拉里昂会被挤坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:30.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需重启之
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让它停下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.39,0:17:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾由山羊五足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.89,0:17:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与狮之首级组成
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通晓远古之学识
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乃魔界哲学大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.56,0:17:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此等小事不值一提
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若想命其停止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:42.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需示吾以胖次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:48.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒爽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉...玲？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:09.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.61,0:18:12.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲 克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉玲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔切克马给我做了缓冲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.62,0:18:17.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.45,0:18:20.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在你上方12米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢...你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你们俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能自己走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 你还摇摇晃晃的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.99,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那边的废物们天差地别
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.49,0:18:59.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既为无能之身 亦为背叛之人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实难以礼相待矣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.41,0:19:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个一点也不可爱的吉祥物是什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:05.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 废物们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.46,0:19:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要出去了 你们可以跟过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.42,0:19:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才不是废物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.92,0:19:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们肯定准备了逃生路线吧 能干的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.55,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.88,0:19:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大水淹过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也撑不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经灌进来这么多水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.35,0:19:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会死在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:26.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很能干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:31.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以像这样准备了紧急用电梯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都进去进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:39.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛痛痛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.68,0:19:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超重了吗 不好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐性胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胖子 胖子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.64,0:19:55.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游泳圈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀呀 真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:04.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等萨哈尔 你想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.49,0:20:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不是那种会牺牲自己的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:12.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后这么做 太狡猾了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.91,0:20:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萨哈尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.80,0:20:23.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乌泽尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.38,0:20:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随意差使你 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.89,0:20:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报酬能等到下次见面时再给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.73,0:20:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没有...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:39.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不凑巧 我没把能卖给你的「和平」随身带着
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.61,0:20:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说也称不上替代品...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:43.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟福音走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,福音 克拉里昂就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让她幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.01,0:21:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「世界和平」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.22,0:21:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的话 总有一天能买到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:28.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 乌泽尔小姐说她没事...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种随心所欲活着的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:34.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能轻易死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种家伙想杀都杀不死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:44.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到地面上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.21,0:21:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得救了吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种小事之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之现在先去安全的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.65,0:22:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下终于能去见昆仑八仙阿姨了
